# 15. Open Questions

The following topics remain open for discussion and future versions of the specification:

* Size of Organisation Number allocation
* Registry governance model
* Organisation registration process
* Reserved numbering ranges
* Learner migration between organisations
* Internationalisation beyond the initial registry
* Long-term sustainability of the registry
